<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="mptm"{.if authenticatedAccount} data-authenticated-account{.end}>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..600;1,9..144,300..500&family=Mulish:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    {squarespace-headers}
  </head>
  <body id="{squarespace.page-id}" class="{squarespace.page-classes}">

    <!-- ============ NAV ============ -->
    <header class="nav" id="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="#top">
          <svg class="mark" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="20" cy="20" r="18.5" stroke="#E6A14F" stroke-width="1.4"/>
            <path d="M11 27c4-1 5-6 9-6s5 5 9 6" stroke="#F0C083" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="20" cy="15" r="3.4" fill="#E6A14F"/>
          </svg>
          Abel Calderon, Jr.
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links" id="navlinks">
          <a href="#book">The Book</a>
          <a href="#pillars">What You'll Discover</a>
          <a href="#author">The Author</a>
          <a href="#community">Community</a>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P8WYMCC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read the Book</a>
        </nav>
        <button class="nav-toggle" id="navtoggle" aria-label="Menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main data-content-field="main-content">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <section class="hero" id="top">
      <!-- Splash background. Replace with your own footage by adding:
           <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="..."> ... </video> -->
      <div class="hero-sky"></div>
      <div class="stars"></div>
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>
      <div class="hero-vignette"></div>

      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy">
            <span class="eyebrow">A book by Abel Calderon, Jr.</span>
            <h1>Spirituality, happiness, and eternal bliss <em>start with you.</em></h1>
            <p class="sub">My Path to Me unites spirituality, love, and personal development through one quiet discovery: the relationship you have with yourself.</p>
            <div class="hero-cta">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P8WYMCC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read on Amazon →</a>
              <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#pillars">Begin the journey</a>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-meta">
              <span class="stars-rating" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
              <span>4.8 average rating · 17 reader reviews on Amazon</span>
            </div>
            <p class="byline">— Abel Calderon, Jr., Esq.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="book" aria-label="My Path to Me book cover">
            <img class="book-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="My Path to Me — book cover by Abel Calderon, Jr.">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scroll-hint"><span>Scroll</span><span class="line"></span></div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ THE PATH / JOURNEY (signature) ============ -->
    <section class="journey" id="book">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="head">
          <span class="eyebrow">The Book</span>
          <h2>Spirituality, lived through <em>four relationships.</em></h2>
          <p>At its heart, My Path to Me explores spirituality — not as a religion, but as the part of us that connects us all. The book walks you through four deepening relationships, and ends with a gentle, practical way to make the journey your own. Whatever your creed, there is a place for you on this path.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="path-wrap">
          <div class="path-line"><div class="path-fill" id="pathfill"></div></div>
          <div class="steps" id="steps">
            <div class="step left">
              <div class="card">
                <span class="num">Chapter One</span>
                <h3>A relationship with myself</h3>
                <p>The journey begins within. Discover the non-physical self — the soul, the spirit — and how meeting it honestly rejuvenates the parts of life that have gone quiet.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="node"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="step right">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="card">
                <span class="num">Chapter Two</span>
                <h3>A relationship with others</h3>
                <p>Spirituality is the gateway to real intimacy. Learn to bring vulnerability and presence to the connections you care about most.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step left">
              <div class="card">
                <span class="num">Chapter Three</span>
                <h3>A relationship with God</h3>
                <p>However you understand it, explore that "something" that connects us all — the source of our spiritual selves — with openness rather than dogma.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="node"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="step right">
              <div class="node"></div>
              <div class="card">
                <span class="num">Chapter Four</span>
                <h3>A relationship with everything</h3>
                <p>Widen the circle outward — to nature and the world around you — until connection becomes a way of moving through life.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step left">
              <div class="card">
                <span class="num">Chapter Five</span>
                <h3>One outline for prayer</h3>
                <p>A warm, practical close: spirituality is like a muscle you train through practice. Pray and meditate from the heart, and let it become an act of love.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="node"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ PILLARS ============ -->
    <section class="pillars" id="pillars">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="eyebrow dim">What You'll Discover</span>
          <h2>Three areas, <em>one relationship</em> at the center</h2>
          <p>My Path to Me illustrates how spirituality, love, and personal development come together through the discovery of your relationship to yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar-grid">
          <article class="pillar spirit reveal">
            <div class="bg"></div>
            <svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F0C083" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v18M5 8c3 0 4 4 7 4s4-4 7-4M5 14c3 0 4 4 7 4s4-4 7-4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            <span class="eyebrow">Spirituality</span>
            <h3>The connecting core</h3>
            <p>Not a religion, but the non-physical part of us that experiences life beyond the five senses — and connects us all. The book treats it with openness, welcoming every reader regardless of creed.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar love reveal">
            <div class="bg"></div>
            <svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F0C083" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 20s-7-4.6-7-10A3.8 3.8 0 0 1 12 7a3.8 3.8 0 0 1 7 3c0 5.4-7 10-7 10z" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span class="eyebrow">Love</span>
            <h3>Deeper relationships</h3>
            <p>Love is the thread running through every relationship in the book — with yourself, with others, and with the Divine. Learn to meet each one with honesty, vulnerability, and presence.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar growth reveal">
            <div class="bg"></div>
            <svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F0C083" stroke-width="1.4" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 21V9m0 0c-3-3-7-2-7-2s-1 5 2 8c2 2 5 1 5 1zm0 0c3-3 7-2 7-2s1 5-2 8c-2 2-5 1-5 1z" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <span class="eyebrow">Personal Development</span>
            <h3>Growth you can practice</h3>
            <p>Spirituality and personal growth are not opposites — they strengthen each other. The book closes with a practical prayer-and-meditation practice you can begin today.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ INSIDE THE BOOK ============ -->
    <section class="inside">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-head">
          <span class="eyebrow dim">Inside My Path to Me</span>
          <h2>What you'll <em>find</em> in these pages</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="inside-grid" id="finds">
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">i</span><p>A clear, inclusive view of <strong>spirituality</strong> — the part of us beyond the five senses that connects us all.</p></div>
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">ii</span><p>The <strong>four relationships</strong> that deepen the journey: with myself, with others, with God, and with everything.</p></div>
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">iii</span><p><strong>Lived stories</strong> from Abel's own journey — how rediscovering spirituality revived areas of life that had gone dormant.</p></div>
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">iv</span><p>How <strong>personal growth and spirituality strengthen each other</strong>, rather than standing in opposition.</p></div>
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">v</span><p>A warm, practical <strong>outline for prayer and meditation</strong> you can begin today — practiced from the heart.</p></div>
          <div class="find"><span class="fnum">vi</span><p>An invitation to <strong>self-discovery</strong> that meets you wherever you are, whatever your creed.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ QUOTE STRIP ============ -->
    <section class="quote">
      <div class="wrap">
        <blockquote>"We are all connected, <span>traveling the same path</span> of personal discovery and enlightenment. Our individual moments differ — but collectively, our life experience is much the same."</blockquote>
        <p class="by">— from the introduction to My Path to Me</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ AUTHOR ============ -->
    <section class="author" id="author">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="author-grid">
          <div class="author-photo reveal">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Abel Calderon, Jr.">
          </div>
          <div class="reveal">
            <span class="eyebrow">About the Author</span>
            <h2>Abel Calderon, <em>Jr.</em></h2>
            <p class="lead">Born and raised in Los Angeles, Abel attended Queen of Angels High School Seminary in San Fernando, St. John's Seminary College in Camarillo, and Southwestern School of Law in Los Angeles.</p>
            <p>He has participated in and coached numerous workshops on leadership, emotional intelligence, and spiritual awareness, eventually creating his own emotional-intelligence workshop focused on spirituality, relationships, and self-love. Today he continues coaching while serving as managing partner attorney at Goldman, Magdalin &amp; Krikes, LLP in Sacramento, California.</p>
            <p>Above all, Abel values his family, his relationships with people from all walks of life, and the journey of self-awareness. He believes that by embracing the spiritual self, every person can create joy, love, and awareness — converting the average into the sacred, acts into expressions, and interactions into deep connections.</p>
            <p style="font-style:italic;color:var(--on-paper-dim);border-left:2px solid var(--dawn);padding-left:18px;margin-top:1.5rem">My Path to Me is dedicated to Abel's son — born of the discovery that, in his loneliest season, loving his child was the truest thing he knew, and the way he found his way back to loving himself, God, and everyone around him.</p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Author &amp; Coach</span>
              <span class="tag">Emotional Intelligence</span>
              <span class="tag">Spiritual Awareness</span>
              <span class="tag">Attorney, Esq.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ COMMUNITY ============ -->
    <section class="community" id="community">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <div class="wrap">
        <span class="eyebrow">Join the Community</span>
        <h2>Begin today — <em>your path is waiting</em></h2>
        <p>Sign up to receive news and updates: special events, training programs, and support for your own journey of self-discovery.</p>
        <form class="signup" id="signup" novalidate>
          <input type="text" name="first" placeholder="First name" aria-label="First name">
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email address" aria-label="Email address" required>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Sign up</button>
        </form>
        <div class="msg" id="signupmsg" role="status"></div>
        <p class="privacy">We will not distribute, sell, or share your information without your written consent. · info@abelcalderon.com</p>
        <div style="margin-top:2.2rem">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P8WYMCC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read My Path to Me on Amazon →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    </main>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="site">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="foot-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="foot-brand">My Path to Me</div>
            <p>Uniting spirituality, love, and personal development through discovering the relationship with yourself.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="foot-cols">
            <div class="foot-col">
              <h4>Explore</h4>
              <a href="#book">The Book</a>
              <a href="#pillars">What You'll Discover</a>
              <a href="#author">The Author</a>
              <a href="#community">Community</a>
            </div>
            <div class="foot-col">
              <h4>Read &amp; Connect</h4>
              <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07P8WYMCC" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Buy on Amazon</a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/mypathtome" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a>
              <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mypathtomebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/368267653761131/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Community Group</a>
            </div>
            <div class="foot-col">
              <h4>Contact</h4>
              <a href="mailto:info@abelcalderon.com">info@abelcalderon.com</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="foot-bottom">
          <span>My Path to Me © 2019 Abel Calderón, Jr. · ISBN 978-0-578-43244-1 · Website © <span id="yr"></span>.</span>
          <span>A journey of self-discovery.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <squarespace:script src="mypathtome.js" combo="false" />
    {squarespace-footers}
  </body>
</html>
